Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:23.72,normal end - tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The world's color turns white
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:29.75,normal end - tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As that which I lost now scatters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:37.22,normal end - tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A voice flows in my heart and falls on my withered soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:42.01,normal end - tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Its timbre​ is one of sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:50.34,normal end - tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The light is being discarded, its wish fading
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:56.87,normal end - tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Being allowed no hope for tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:01:02.50,normal end - tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As my tears fall in the shadows of these memories
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:08.84,normal end - tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I embrace the warmth conveyed by our superposed hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:12.89,normal end - tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(45,695)}Without even knowing the meaning of love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:17.59,normal end - tl,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(45,695)}And as I gently snuggle up to you again
